<h1>wordpress plugin development for form builder</h1>  <p>how to develop a form builder plug in that </p>  <ol> <li>builds form and control on the fly  </li> <li>which lets additional css class to be added</li> <li>which performs form validations as well</li> <li>provides captch security</li> </ol>  <p>in addition to all this i wish to have  notifications (if visitor posted query) on the dash board  to indicate     </p>  <ol> <li>Number of queries have been received from visitors   </li> <li>if i click on notifications it shows all data in tabular form</li> <li>filterable by dates, query type, answered, read, not answered etc</li> </ol>